channel.title: KiwiiScape Client! With Gameframe! First Client!
channel.description: Hey guys, I'm Uploading my own KiwiiScape Client right now. It'll be on MEDIAFIRE so don't ask where's virus scan.. Anyway This client is partly Richscape/ricscape based. CREDITS: Me ( 50% ) Jamming songs coding a few things changing d chain to dplate :) and adding a few models. Rich ( 5% ) First base. Ric914 ( 5% ) Secondary base. Ibcrootbeer ( 30% ) a few Sprites and for Inspiring me about what I could do by showing us all what he could do :) Thanks Sean. Johnny Str ( 10% ) For also Inspiring me and for also helping me get the picture. :P A Pic. [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/116qbn6.jpg[/img] NOTE: This is an Open editing source. And I will be adding extra models, npcs and other crap to it. DOWNLOAD LINK: http://www.mediafire.com/file/mz4zzynmmjz/Project KiwiiScape.rar This also includes that fully sick song by Flo rida. I know its not orginaled from flo but he made it better.... The song: Right Round - Flo rida. Please Do not flame as it is my first client and also PM me if download link is broken. Please Post and cheer me on ..
